result.title: Online Judge for APIO problems
result.content:
My first time to write blog.

APIO 2014 will be held in a few days, so I want to solve the past exams.

But I can't find any online judge for APIO 2011, 2010, and so on.

Where can I submit my code for these problems?

Just for your information:

online judge for APIO 2013 (without taskauthor) : http://koj.miz-miz.biz/problem_list (in

Japanese, and this judge was made by kagamiz)

online judge for APIO 2012 : http://open.apio2012.ioi-jp.org/
